ğŸ” Burger Shop Application

A Java Swing-based desktop application that simulates a simple Burger Shop system.
Built with NetBeans IDE and Java Swing GUI, this project demonstrates fundamental software engineering concepts such as GUI design, event handling, object-oriented programming specially the importance of encapsulation, and user interaction.

